<li><a href="Anarcho-capitalism" title="Anarcho-capitalism">Anarcho-capitalism</a></li>
<li><a href="../../w/index-title=Cooperative_capitalism&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Cooperative capitalism (page does not exist)">Cooperative capitalism</a></li>
<li><a href="Crony_capitalism" title="Crony capitalism">Crony capitalism</a></li>
<li><a href="Finance_capitalism" title="Finance capitalism">Finance capitalism</a></li>
</ul>
</td>
<td style="width: 33.33%;" align="left" valign="top">
<ul>
<li><a href="Financial_capitalism" title="Financial capitalism">Financial capitalism</a></li>
<li><a href="Late_capitalism" title="Late capitalism">Late capitalism</a></li>
<li><a href="Neo-capitalism" title="Neo-capitalism" class="mw-redirect">Neo-capitalism</a></li>
</ul>
</td>
<td style="width: 33.33%;" align="left" valign="top">
