<li id="cite_note-rogetfreeenterprise-19"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-rogetfreeenterprise_19-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-rogetfreeenterprise_19-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-rogetfreeenterprise_19-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">"free enterprise." Roget's 21st Century Thesaurus, Third Edition. Philip Lief Group 2008.</span></li>
